text: Sandra Donnelly (born 26 September 1969) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Calgary
